    '📊 Sheet: ' + cfg.SHEET_NAME + ' (headers on row ' + cfg.HEADER_ROW + ')\n' +
    '🔘 Trigger: column "' + cfg.COL_TRIGGER + '" = YES\n' +
    '🔤 Aliases: ' + cfg.ALIASES_JSON,
    ui.ButtonSet.OK);
